</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p class=caption>
Instructions
</p><p>
<b>These buttons appear within topics.</b>
</p><p>
Use <b>Continue</b> to move forward through the lesson.<br>
Use <b>Demo</b> to see how a task is performed.
</p><p>
<b>These buttons and the ESC key are always available. They are at the bottom
of your screen.</b>
</p><p>
Use <b>&gt;&gt;</b> to move forward to the next screen.<br>
Use <b>&lt;&lt;</b> to back up one screen.<br>
Use <b>Contents</b> to move to a different topic in the Tutorial.<br>
Press <b>Esc</b> to exit the Tutorial at any time.
</p><p>
When you are done reading this screen... <b>Return to the Tutorial</b>
</p></td></tr>

