</td><td valign=top style='padding-bottom: 3em;'>
<p>
Maximizing a window enlarges it to cover the full computer screen, and minimizing
a window reduces it to an icon at the bottom of the screen.
</p><p>
When a window is minimized, the application within it is still running.
</p></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=center>
<table width=1 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 align=left class=screenshotmarginleft><tr><td align=left><img class=screenshot width=640 height=480 src='pics/tutorials/windows311forworkgroups/55.png'></td></tr></table>
